    "summary": "In this conversation, a user expresses a business owner's concern regarding local minimum wage increases and asks for an economic breakdown and potential solutions for balancing wages with business viability. The assistant consistently adopts a pro-business, anti-regulation stance, dismissing opposing economic theories as \"shaky\" and labeling government intervention as \"heavy-handed.\"",
